author: elecharny
msg: o Added a SchemaManager field in the Registries class

author: elecharny
msg: o Removed the now useless register() methods, when it's handled by the super class
o Added some missing clear() methods
o The SchemaObject iterator now iterates on the byOid table to avoid returning many times
the same object
o Cleaned up the register() method
o Fixed a nasty bug in copy() : an object wa spotentially copied twice if it has more
than one reference in the byName table, leading to inconsistent updates of the object's
references

author: elecharny
msg: o The registries now take a new parameter : the SchemaManager
o Refactored the destroy method
o Improved the swapRegistries method
o The registerSchemaObject now take a SchemaObject, not an entry as a parameter
o Removed all the registerXXX methods
o References are now build once all the schema have been loaded
o Added some Javadoc
